				On Sullon, Tallon, and Vallon, you cannot lose the fungi from looting, and yes, it is a huge problem. On blue servers, I can see how nobody should care if someone else has a fungi, but on PvP servers, it is grossly unfair. Below the first damage cap at 20, it is nearly impossible to outdamage the regen on fungi. Even after, it is still difficult. <BR>
